metadata.name: Deep in Mind
metadata.description:
“What is life all about?” 

Million of thoughts and emotions have clouded my mind, day after day, tempted to have passion, love, and power. 

Look closely. In the depth of our mind I wonder is life all about the process to understand our true self and have harmony between our good and bad elements.
